Class PPGraphic

  • java.lang.Object
    • gui.PPGraphic

  • public class PPGraphic
extends java.lang.Object
    A PPGraphic stores a Shape, Color, and Stroke to be used for drawing the graphic in PowerPaint.

    30 October 2014
    Author:
